 Academy Award for Best Actress and Stevenson was nominated for Best Director. His other Disney films include the first two Herbie films, The Love Bug (1968) and Herbie Rides Again (1974), as well as Bedknobs and Broomsticks (1971). Three of his films featured English actor David Tomlinson. Source: Wikidata; 01/08/2023", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-02-26T20:31:02.998612+11:00", "external_links": [{"id": 5040, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Stevenson_(filmmaker)"}], "uuid": "518c695b-146b-4892-8a1d-fe565033615d", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "27889", "external_references": [{"id": 25784, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q725060"}, {"id": 31218, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "76501576"}, {"id": 31219, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "no92028191"}, {"id": 31220, "source": {"name": "WorldCat", "slug": "worldcat"}, "source_identifier": "lccn-no92028191"}], "date_modified": "2025-02-26T20:31:02.998928+11:00"}